title: Doctor Who - Big Finish Podcast 01 - 02-05-2008
description:
Big Finish Podcast - Episode 1
(05/02/2008)
In the first Big Finish Podcast Executive Producer Nicholas Briggs takes us through some of his favourite moments from upcoming stories, with clips from The Condemned, The Dark Husband and Grand Theft Cosmos - and there&#039;s also a few words from Dark Husband writer David Quantick. Plus Nick reveals what we can expect from the future of Big Finish downloads, and explains some of the reasons for the pricing structures.
